name: PhiBrows Universal Holder
short_description: PhiBrows Universal holder is a perfect replacement for Classic and Eccentric holders. Now you can be sure all the blades will fit into one holder! Suitable for all blades.Made of:Stainless steelSuitable for autoclave. Proper sterilisation after every usage is obligatory.
